# Dev: leave unset — Vite proxies /api and /socket.io to :3000 (localhost + phone on LAN).
# Production (Vercel): required — set in Project → Settings → Environment Variables, then redeploy.
# Example: https://venue-pos-api.onrender.com  (your Render web service URL, no trailing slash)
# VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:3000
